extends ../../wrapper
block content
  .card.section
    .card-header.secondary-color.white-text
      h2.card-title Cards
    .card-body
        p.
          Cards are a convenient means of displaying content composed of
          different types of objects. Theyâ€™re also well-suited for presenting
          similar objects whose size or supported actions can vary considerably,
          like photos with captions of variable length.
  .section
    h2 Basic Card
    .grid
      .cell.cell-5.card
        .card-body.primary-color.white-text
          h2.card-title Card Title
          p I am a very simple card. I am good at containing small bits of information. I am convenient because I require little markup to be used effectively.
    pre: code.language-html
      ='<div class="grid">\n'
      ='  <div class="cell cell-5 card">\n'
      ='    <div class="card-body primary-color white-text">\n'
      ='      <h2 class="card-title">Card Title</h2>\n'
      ='      <p>I am a very simple card. I am good at containing small bits of information. I am convenient because I require little markup to be used effectively.</p>\n'
      ='    </div>\n'
      ='  </div>\n'
      ='</div>'
  .section
    h2 Header Card
    style.
      #card-example2 .card-header {
        background-image: url(https://static.pexels.com/photos/87646/horsehead-nebula-dark-nebula-constellation-orion-87646.jpeg);
      }
    .grid
      .cell.cell-5.card#card-example2
        .card-header.white-text
          h2.card-title Card Title
        .card-body
          p I am a simple card with a header and a body. With a background image I stand out more than other headers and convey what I am about.
    pre: code.language-html
      ='<style>\n'
      ='  #card-example2 .card-header {\n'
      ='      background-image: url(https://static.pexels.com/photos/87646/horsehead-nebula-dark-nebula-constellation-orion-87646.jpeg);\n'
      ='  }\n'
      ='</style>\n'
      ='<div class="grid">\n'
      ='  <div id="card-example2" class="cell cell-5 card">\n'
      ='    <div class="card-header white-text">\n'
      ='      <h2 class="card-title">Card Title</h2>\n'
      ='    </div>\n'
      ='    <div class="card-body">\n'
      ='      <p>I am a simple card with a header and a body. With a background image I stand out more than other headers and convey what I am about.</p>\n'
      ='    </div>\n'
      ='  </div>\n'
      ='</div>'
  .section
    h2 Call-to-Action Card
    p.
      A call-to-action card is a card that has an actions section where the user can select an action.
      By default actions align to the right, see below on how to move the actions to the left.
    h5 Actions on Bottom
    .grid
      .cell.cell-5.card
        .card-body
          p Would you like to continue?
        .card-actions
          a.btn Yes
          a.btn No
    pre: code.language-html
      ='<div class="grid">\n'
      ='  <div class="cell cell-5 card">\n'
      ='    <div class="card-body">\n'
      ='      <p>Would you like to continue?</p>\n'
      ='    </div>\n'
      ='    <div class="card-actions"><a class="btn">Yes</a><a class="btn">No</a></div>\n'
      ='  </div>\n'
      ='</div>'
    h5 Actions on Top
    .grid
      .cell.cell-5.card
        .card-actions
          a: i.material-icons close
        .card-body
          p You are not allowed in here!
    pre: code.language-html
      ='<div class="grid">\n'
      ='  <div class="cell cell-5 card">\n'
      ='    <div class="card-actions"><a class="btn">Yes</a><a class="btn">No</a></div>\n'
      ='    <div class="card-body">\n'
      ='      <p>Would you like to continue?</p>\n'
      ='    </div>\n'
      ='  </div>\n'
      ='</div>'
    h5 Actions to the Left
    p.
      Actions can be moved to the left using #[code .card-actions-left].
    .grid
      .cell.cell-5.card
        .card-body
          p Would you like to continue?
        .card-actions.card-actions-left
          a.btn Yes
          a.btn No
    pre: code.language-html
      ='<div class="grid">\n'
      ='  <div class="cell cell-5 card">\n'
      ='    <div class="card-body">\n'
      ='      <p>Would you like to continue?</p>\n'
      ='    </div>\n'
      ='    <div class="card-actions card-actions-left"><a class="btn">Yes</a><a class="btn">No</a></div>\n'
      ='  </div>\n'
      ='</div>'
  .section
    h2 Card Sizes
    p.
      By adding #[code .card-sm], #[code .card-md] or #[code .card-lg] to a card, you can limit the size of the card.
      The card body will start to scroll if the content extends past the maximum height.
    .grid.grid-space-between
      .cell.cell-3
        .card.card-sm
          .card-header.primary-color.white-text
            h2.card-title Small Card
          .card-body
            p I am a small card with a header height of 175px and a total maximum height of 325px.
      .cell.cell-3
        .card.card-md
          .card-header.primary-color.white-text
            h2.card-title Medium Card
          .card-body
            p I am a medium card with a header height of 225px and a total maximum height of 425px.
      .cell.cell-3
        .card.card-lg
          .card-header.primary-color.white-text
            h2.card-title large Card
          .card-body
            p I am a large card with a header height of 275px and a total maximum height of 525px.
